    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the VAD hemolysis CFD model at MRL 5 has been reviewed. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were assessed; assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels in five cases. Six factors remain unassessed. The Monte Carlo UQ provides partial uncertainty quantification. The team accepts the package for submission pending resolution of open factors in the next assessment cycle.",
